Author: Rolf Simoes [aut, cre], Brian Pondi [aut], OpenGeoHub Foundation [cph]
Maintainer: Rolf Simoes <rolf.simoes@opengeohub.org>
Description: Provides an R framework for crafting and serving openEO API
    applications by building on the plumber package. The friendly and
    extensible interface helps create RESTful openEO web services that
    prioritise ease of use, scalability, and flexibility.
